%html
  %head
    %meta{content: 'text/html; charset=UTF-8', :'http-equiv' => 'Content-Type'}
  %body
    %h1 DEF CON CTF Password Reset
    :markdown
      Hello #{@user.username.inspect}!

      Somebody has started the password reset process by entering your
      email address on the DEF CON CTF Qualifications website.

      ## Yes, Reset Your Password

      Visit the password reset interface at:

      [#{@url}](#{@url})

      This will allow you to change your password.

      ## No, Don't Reset Your Password

      Log in to the qualifications website:

      [#{root_url}](#{root_url})

      Click on the "Account" link at the top-left.

      Click the "Disavow Password Resets" button.
